OL,3,CThree teenagers arrested following
OL,4,CPaignton train station fire
OL,6,FThree teenage boys have been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of Arson following a fire
OL,8,Fat Paignton train station yesterday.
OL,10,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService was called to reports of a
OL,12,Ffire at the station shortly before 6am
OL,13,Fon Tuesday 21 July.
OL,15,FThe blaze was extinguished and no
OL,16,Finjuries were reported.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
