OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784884711
OL,3,CThree teenagers arrested following
OL,4,CPaignton train station fire
OL,6,FThe fire caused trains to be cancelled
OL,7,Fbetween Newton Abbot and Paignton and
OL,8,Fservices from Exeter St David's had to
OL,9,Fterminate at Newton Abbot, meaning
OL,10,Ftrains were unable to call at Torre,
OL,11,FTorquay, or Paignton.
OL,13,FThe boys, aged 13, 15 and 16 were
OL,14,Farrested on Tuesday 21 July in the
OL,15,FPaignton area.
OL,17,FThey were taken to police custody and
OL,18,Fwere questioned by detectives. They
OL,19,Fhave now been released on conditional
OL,20,Fbail while enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/2
